{"tid":1499870,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"愛女險死韋素即離中國","createTime":"2019-08-24T01:52:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T03:21:14.000Z","uid":21309,"like":105,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"81b2431d38a5190f38e8816523a26e32e062b495","tid":1499870,"uid":21309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:52:56.000Z","msg":"比利時中場上年離開天津權健加盟多蒙特，佢最近接受訪問就講到離開權健嘅原因。韋素話︰「有次我個女肚痛，我哋去到醫院後診斷出係腸阻塞，不過醫院設備唔夠，要去天津或者北京更大型嘅醫院，病情太危急下我決定去較鄰近嘅醫院。」不過之後先係噩夢嘅開始︰「到咗之後，我哋要輪籌等叫名，你唔會想像到居然有咁多人等緊睇醫生。我哋就喺嗰度等咗成兩、三個鐘，去到凌晨先見到醫生。」呢件事之後，韋素決定離開中國，佢仲話，搵幾多錢都好，人身安全最緊要。<br />\n<br />\n俾外國人見識下大陸嘅醫療體系<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb27d3ecf0945c23ec260151567b0327a1d1bf61","tid":1499870,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:56:45.000Z","msg":"權健有咁多養生保健品佢唔用要去排醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"e60baf57e19da7b421302b84d440aaa0e96b71b6","tid":1499870,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:00:00.000Z","msg":"回頭是岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569bcef8dc33a0ef63a3569425c85604ad76ae0c","tid":1499870,"uid":3028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:00:16.000Z","msg":"兩三個鍾咪算快囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b398e13c970b2b01b67921432443b30560e43e37","tid":1499870,"uid":7550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:02:40.000Z","msg":"香港排急症仲耐呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba3cc0f5e6e4759c1ad88eb418853905a7a08ef","tid":1499870,"uid":12991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:05:06.000Z","msg":"要炒籌呀<br />\n一係科水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ec75dc69c38efdab4ddebbe0216edb7a189839","tid":1499870,"uid":172192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:05:38.000Z","msg":"排過急症表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b0dbd40be90a11e8222af4c89420e6cf1b67d1","tid":1499870,"uid":29627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:06:03.000Z","msg":"比錢就得啦<br />\n駛乜輪籌"},{"pid":"dcdf3426b54ebbfae2238ec311fe862b831e76a9","tid":1499870,"uid":26953,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:07:54.000Z","msg":"唔比定錢先吊鹽水吊足你個女一個禮拜都仲得啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f25718854928335fee668836053c109c52629d","tid":1499870,"uid":137569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:13:14.000Z","msg":"佢要吵先有得先睇<br />\n我哋住開所謂發達地區嘅係好難適應"},{"pid":"cc429f9a4a2e1fbe51242e510820ee800952922b","tid":1499870,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:14:08.000Z","msg":"腸阻塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57057223add12c7599cb1ebe834dd4bc2775e138","tid":1499870,"uid":143768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:16:57.000Z","msg":"佢攞籌之前係咪唔記得塞幾舊水俾人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f71f5f0a6f5512f7d26a8f22beda532d030e4a","tid":1499870,"uid":31906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b398e13c970b2b01b67921432443b30560e43e37","tid":1499870,"uid":7550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:02:40.000Z","msg":"香港排急症仲耐呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:25:55.000Z","msg":"有錢可以睇私家既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b041b0ab2d57da9ea5716a621d1367ec7de27ad","tid":1499870,"uid":248556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:45:33.000Z"